  <text>
      <body>
         <head type="metadata"><name type="person" corresp="#JH">Julian Hawthorne</name> to
            <addressee><name type="person">Samuel L. Clemens</name></addressee>
            <lb/><date when="1884-03-31">31 March 1884</date> &#x2022; <name type="place">Sag Harbor, N.Y.</name>   
            <sourceline>(MS: <ref type="citeref" corresp="#CU-MARK">CU-MARK</ref>, UCLC 41951)</sourceline></head>
         
         <div1 type="letter">
            <opener><dateline rend="indentdateline"><name type="place">Sag Harbor L. I.</name><space extent="2"/>
               <lb/><date when="1884-03-31">March 31<hi rend="superscript">st</hi> 1884</date>
               </dateline>
               <salute rend="noindent">My dear Clemens</salute>
               </opener>
            <p rend="text-indent:2">I have an idea of following the prevailing fashion, and starting an autograph book: and by way of benediction to the enterprise, I wish to begin with yours. I may never get beyond that: but even then I shall have half ended what was so well begun. If you can find nothing better to do therefore, do sit down and dash me off <pb facs="hawthorne02.jpg" xml:id="pb002" n="2"/> something characteristic and brilliant and meanwhile believe me</p>
            <closer>
               <salute rend="indentcompclose">Always cordially yours</salute>
               <signed rend="indentsig"><hi rend="paraph">Julian Hawthorne</hi>.</signed>
            <lb/>Saml. Clemens Esq.</closer>
         </div1>
         
         <div1 type="post-transmission">
            <div2 type="envelope">
               <ab>Samuel Clemens Esq. | Hartford | Conn.</ab>
               <ab><note xml:id="ed001" type="ed" place="inline">postmarked:</note> <hi rend="xs-smallcaps">sag <corr>har</corr>bor apr 1 1884 n. y.</hi></ab>
               <ab><note type="ed" xml:id="ed002" place="inline">docketed by SLC, in pencil:</note> Julian Hawthorne</ab>
            </div2>
         </div1>
         <div1 xml:id="cm0001" type="commentary"/>        
         
